quran[25]{c,v,t}:
  40,41,O my people dum ego invite vos saved vos invite me hellfire
  40,42,Vos invite me est unappreciative de DEUS set Eum idols ego non recognize. Ego inviting vos Almighty Forgiver
  40,43,Ibi est non doubt ut quod vos invite me perfecit non habet basis in hoc saeculum nor in Hereafter ut noster ultimate return est to DEUS ut transgressors incurred hellfire
  40,44,Some feria vos remember quod ego telling vos statim Ego sinister judgment hoc matter DEUS; DEUS est Seer totus people
  40,45,DEUS TUNC protected EUM EX their MALUS schemes DUM people Pharaoh incurred MALUS retribution
  40,46,"Hell shown them feria ac nox, Feria Resurrection Admit Pharaoh's people into malus retribution"
  40,47,Prout they argue Hell followers dictus to their dux Nos perfecit used to tuus followers est vos spare nos any part hoc Hell
  40,48,Dux dictus Nos est totus in hoc unus. DEUS SCABINUS among the people
  40,49,Those in hellfire dictus to tutor Hell Alias tuus Dominus reduce retribution nos et unus feria
  40,50,They dictus Perfecit vos non receive tuus messengers delivered vos clear messages They reply Sic nos perfecit. They dictus Tunc implore vos wish imploring de disbelievers est semper in vain
  40,51,multus assuredly nos dedit victory noster messengers those believe ambo in hoc saeculum feria testis summoned
  40,52,Ut feria apologies disbelievers non benefit them. They incurred condemnation; they incurred malus destiny
  40,53,Nos dedit Moses guidance factus Infans Israel inherit scripture
  40,54,(Their history) est lesson reminder those possess intelligence
  40,55,Ergo est patient deus promise est true ask forgiveness tuus sin glorify praise tuus Dominus nox feria
  40,56,Surely those qui argue deus revelations proof est exposing arrogance hidden their chests they est non et aware de it Ergo seek refuge DEUS; He est Hearer Seer
  40,57,creation de caelum terra est et awesome than creation human est multus people non know
  40,58,Non aequalis est blind seer. Nor est those believe work righteousness aequalis to sinners! Rarely perfecit vos take heed
  40,59,multus certainly Hora (Feria Judgment advenit non doubt de it multus people non believe)
  40,60,Tuus Dominus dictus Implore Me ego respond vos! Surely those est too arrogant worship Me iniit Gehenna forcibly
  40,61,DEUS EST UNUS designed NOX ITA VOS rest it FERIA lighted. DEUS bestows MULTUS blessings people MULTUS people NON est thankful
  40,62,Such est DEUS tuus Dominus Creator totus things. ibi non est deus absque He! Quam vos deviate
  40,63,Deviating est those disregard deus revelations
  40,64,DEUS EST UNUS rendered TERRA habitable PRO VOS CAELUM formidable structure He designed VOS designed VOS BENE. He est Unus provisus vos bonus provisions Such est DEUS tuus Dominus; Exalted est DEUS Dominus universe
  40,65,He est Vivus; ibi non est deus absque He! Vos worship Eum alone devoting tuus religionis absolutely Eum alone Praise est DEUS Dominus universe